title: Martial Law!
subtitle: Hitler has called the army in to restore order
view-if: president == "Hitler" and resisted_hitler and time == panic_time
tags: event
new-page: true
on-arrival: reichswehr_loyalty -= 0.05 if reichswehr_loyalty >= 0.05; reichswehr_loyalty = 0 if reichswehr_loyalty < 0.05; reichswehr_loyalty -= 0.05 if judicial_reform < 2; reichswehr_loyalty = 0 if reichswehr_loyalty < 0

= Martial Law!

Following his failure to consolidate power by taking over Prussia, Hitler has, in a state of panic, resorted to calling an illegal state of martial law over Germany.

- @nah: Yeah as if.

@nah
subtitle: It's time for a civil war showdown.

We mobilize the Reichsbanner to meet the SA in the streets as the Reichswehr is called out of its barracks to fight us. [? if judicial_reform >= 2 : The courts strike down the martial law, handing us legitimacy. ?][? if judicial_reform < 2 : The courts certify the martial law, but we know they're illegitimate. ?]

- @civil_war: It is a civil war.